description: Demolition of the existing building and erection of two buildings of 17 and 7 storeys linked by a central podium for use as 121 residential units (Class C3); dual/alternative use of part of the ground floor as a cafe/restaurant/gallery (Class A1/A3/D1); three levels of basement including car parking and plant area; replacement stair linking the river walk with Vauxhall Bridge and other associated works to the river walk and adjacent public landscape; works of hard and soft landscaping and other works incidental to the application.
